description: Excellent investment opportunity, leased through 6/1/2026 at $5,800 per month! Luxurious three bedroom, two-bath residence with the convenience of GARAGE PARKING in the vibrant neighborhood of South Boston! 321 On Broadway, a boutique elevator building completed in late 2021, nestled in the heart of South Boston’s West Side. This exquisite home offers three bedrooms, private outdoor space with roof rights, and top-tier finishes, including wide plank engineered oak flooring, Bosch stainless steel appliances, Calcatta Quartz countertops and backsplash, and ample storage. The thoughtfully designed floor plan provide three queen-sized bedrooms and master suites featuring floating vanities and beautifully tiled en-suite bath. Elevator access, garage parking, and additional storage are among the many conveniences offered. Ideally situated mere steps from the Broadway T station, CVS pharmacy, Foodies Supermarket, Caffe Nero, and local dining options.
